sections.heading: and reports; department; duties
sections.text: The Department of Health and Human Services shall prescribe the tests, the test methods and techniques, and such reports and reporting procedures as are necessary to implement sections 71-519 to 71-524.SourceLaws 1987, LB 385, ยง 3;Laws 1996, LB 1044, ยง 504;Laws 2002,
